#)XML VS Java Configuration
--> “XML configuration uses XML files to define beans,  
    while Java configuration uses Java classes with annotations like @Configuration and @Bean.
--> Java config is cleaner, type-safe, and used in modern Spring Boot.
--> XML is older and mainly found in legacy applications.”

